# GitNexus scan scope for nano-vllm.
# Default-deny, then include source, tests, and high-signal repo context.
*
!*/

# Product source and runnable scripts
!nanovllm/*.py
!nanovllm/**/*.py
!example.py
!bench.py

# Tests, including future nested test packages
!tests/*.py
!tests/**/*.py
!test/*.py
!test/**/*.py
!**/tests/*.py
!**/tests/**/*.py
!**/__tests__/*.py
!**/__tests__/**/*.py
!test_*.py
!*_test.py
!**/test_*.py
!**/*_test.py

# High-signal project context for code intelligence
!pyproject.toml
!README.md
!AGENTS.md
!CLAUDE.md

# Generated/runtime state and non-code assets stay out of the index
.planning/**
.omx/**
.gitnexus/**
.code-review-graph/**
graphify-out/**
.git/**
__pycache__/**
*.pyc
assets/**
